sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Client
    participant A as Workflow API
    participant G as Generator
    participant D as Hasura DB

    C->>A: Upload source file
    A->>D: Insert Draft & Event
    D-->>A: Draft ID
    A->>G: Generate JSON
    G-->>A: PassageExamDoc
    A->>D: Update Draft
    
    C->>A: Review & Edit
    A->>D: Update Draft JSON
    
    C->>A: Publish Draft
    A->>D: Fetch Categories
    A->>D: Check duplicate
    
    alt Is Duplicate
        A-->>C: Skip or Fail
    else Is New
        Note right of A: Atomic DB insert:<br/>materials, exams,<br/>questions, hotspots
        A->>D: Insert exam mutation
        D-->>A: Insert Success
        A->>D: Update Draft status
        A-->>C: PublishResult
    end
